  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HYNPYTOL</strong> ([heen-pee-tol] meaning \"<i>white blood cell</i>\" in Korean) is a <strong>retro-themed puzzle action adventure game</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to save a crumbling <strong>immune system</strong> as a chosen \"<strong>Killer T</strong>\", guided by a rather grumpy \"<strong>Dendritic</strong>\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A simple yet versatile \"high-five\" action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this perilous world, all that the \"Killer T\" can do is \"<strong>high-five</strong>\". </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to <strong>use your hand</strong> for everything: from moving around and talking to other cells, to overcoming obstacles and taking care of infection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.poster.avif?t=1769544712\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.webm?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.mp4?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A reimagniation of the 90's visuals and sounds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HYNPYTOL is inspired by the pixel graphics and sounds of <strong>90's games</strong>, and reimagines them with a modern touch for a unique charm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this nostalgic world; you may also find some <strong>easter eggs</strong> along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.poster.avif?t=1769544712\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.webm?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.mp4?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The immune system: separating \"you\" from \"us\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the human body and the various mechanisms of the immune system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn all about your friends and enemies in the <strong>immunopedia</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/f707a4abd85fc518c383e341238fee57.avif?t=1769544712\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras_big/f707a4abd85fc518c383e341238fee57.avif?t=1769544712 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HYNPYTOL</strong> ([heen-pee-tol] meaning \"<i>white blood cell</i>\" in Korean) is a <strong>retro-themed puzzle action adventure game</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to save a crumbling <strong>immune system</strong> as a chosen \"<strong>Killer T</strong>\", guided by a rather grumpy \"<strong>Dendritic</strong>\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A simple yet versatile \"high-five\" action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this perilous world, all that the \"Killer T\" can do is \"<strong>high-five</strong>\". </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to <strong>use your hand</strong> for everything: from moving around and talking to other cells, to overcoming obstacles and taking care of infection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.poster.avif?t=1769544712\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.webm?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6df8ac9f8fe535142691b0b8d33180f5.mp4?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A reimagniation of the 90's visuals and sounds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HYNPYTOL is inspired by the pixel graphics and sounds of <strong>90's games</strong>, and reimagines them with a modern touch for a unique charm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this nostalgic world; you may also find some <strong>easter eggs</strong> along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.poster.avif?t=1769544712\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.webm?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/6eb782cc7a01fca10a64b2518c2c957c.mp4?t=1769544712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The immune system: separating \"you\" from \"us\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the human body and the various mechanisms of the immune system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn all about your friends and enemies in the <strong>immunopedia</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras/f707a4abd85fc518c383e341238fee57.avif?t=1769544712\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2520000/extras_big/f707a4abd85fc518c383e341238fee57.avif?t=1769544712 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
